\end_inset

,
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $K(X\upto n)-n$
\end_inset

 converges to infinity.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Proof
Clearly,
 (c) implies (b).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
(b) implies (a):
 We show that,
