 we can place an upper bound on the complexity of infinitely many prefixes of 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

.
 So,
 let 
\begin_inset Formula $U_{n}$
\end_inset

 be a Martin-Löf test that 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

