\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

-th string of length 
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{N}$
\end_inset

 has complexity bounded above by:
 
\begin_inset Formula $\length{\sigma}+c+\log k$
\end_inset

.
 Now,
 if we have 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

