 if 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 is the leftmost element of 
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
K(X\upto d)\leq\abs{\sigma}+c+(d-n).
\]

\end_inset

Now,
