\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

?
 (This would imply not computable for infinitely many 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

.)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
I was being silly.
 Thanks Denis.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proposition
If 
